[Scene:
  * Trunk of a man on a hospital bed
  * Daily calendar and clock on wall
  * Chair
  * Door
]

[A knock at the door.]

Man (with mock drama): Enter...

[A nurse enters, flips the calendar to the next day and sets to
tending the man.]

Nurse: Good morning.

Man: Good morning.

Nurse: Sleep well?

Man: No better or worse than usual.
